  --------------

   This program should be published on every public medium, as long as all
   files  in  the  archive  are  unchanged. If this medium is a CD, then I
   expect a free copy. (AminetCDs excluded)

   @{b}Execute64 is Smurfware.@{ub} If decided  to  publish  the  full  version  of
   Execute64,  because  I  hope that every one who likes my work is paying
   the fee!

   I expect that anyone who uses Execute64 regularly is  @{"registering" link "HOWTOREGISTER"}  for
   my tool. I think this don“t hurts anybody.

   @{b}I am not liable for injures or data loss caused by Execute64.  The  use
   of Execute64 is on your own responsibility !!!@{ub}
@endnode
